{"tid":780250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈 要結左婚都重同老豆老母住嘅男人係垃圾","createTime":"2018-08-15T04:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:25:28.000Z","uid":77473,"like":663,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"e51b539c0fa10715d5580d1058b7655c3b7586d3","tid":780250,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:36:17.000Z","msg":"冇錢買樓都有錢租樓掛 <br />\n又講埋晒咩同老豆老母住主先  易啲上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你做鴨服侍富婆夠易啲儲錢上車啦 你唔做？<br />\n<br />\n嗰個係你老豆老母你緊係住得舒服啦<br />\n話屋企人好易相處啦<br />\n有人服侍 左擁右抱 <br />\n又有老婆又有老母照顧<br />\n<br />\n要屈就自已老婆對住一堆陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日搞到婆媳 姑嫂糾紛<br />\n返工已經辛苦 放工重要睇奶奶面口<br />\n扑嘢就要就住就住<br />\n<br />\n明知自已窮 養唔起老婆仔女就咪撚拍拖 <br />\n浪費人青春時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撚係就一早18歲排定公屋"},{"pid":"840a6b48b0dad4856e14adde465fe89997183760","tid":780250,"uid":77473,"like":30,"dislike":292,"score":-262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:37:42.000Z","msg":"重有 肯同老爺奶缴住嘅女人都係cheap 女人"},{"pid":"2d6951e0ad313b7318c184c4da6afaeb947c9013","tid":780250,"uid":77473,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重有 肯同老爺奶奶住嘅女人都係cheap 女人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31e5f5cda39eabaae151b6c4ed9e673e11e67629","tid":780250,"uid":117584,"like":88,"dislike":18,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"我鐘意啊吹尻<br />\n<br />\n利申:未結婚"},{"pid":"31788af91ebb6c1dc89686494f23b0565efac313","tid":780250,"uid":112416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"買左樓花未入得伙嘛"},{"pid":"9ab3b236dbeede09f9d893f9aef1d855ed4a79a2","tid":780250,"uid":77473,"like":1,"dislike":52,"score":-51,"quote":{"pid":"31788